-- Tullow Gets Conditional Approval From Uganda for Heritage Asset Purchase
-- Fred Ojambo
-- 2010-07-06T13:38:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/tullow-gets-conditional-approval-for-purchase-of-heritage-assets-in-uganda.html

          
          
             Tullow Oil Plc said its purchase of
assets in Uganda from Heritage Oil Plc was approved by the
government.  
 “It has been approved conditionally” on the basis that
Heritage pays due taxes, Brian Glover, Tullow’s country manager
for Uganda, said by phone.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
 fojambo@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        